data.name: textl1.Text
data.value: Sets the language of the launcher's user interface. The changed language setting will be used after it is restarted.

data.name: textl2.Text
data.value: Sets the language that the game displayed in. You can also set the country code of the server.

data.name: label2.Text
data.value: When you configure it, the game is carried out automaticly after an update.

data.name: label4.Text
data.value: Specify here the ip/dns of your login server and the port of it .

data.name: label9.Text
data.value: You can put here many options about the news banner. Also, you can specify extra options for the game client.

data.name: label6.Text
data.value: Specify here the url path of your patches. You can also force the patch update.
